data.description: Discover Southwest Bakersfield living with this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom Balfanz home boasting stunning curb appeal. The upgraded kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, seamlessly connects to the formal living area. Three guest bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an indoor utility room add practicality. The master suite offers luxury with an XL closet and a bathroom featuring dual vanities, a walk-in shower, and a soaking tub. Modern amenities include a tankless water heater, solar panels, and RV parking. Outside, a covered patio and spacious grass area invite relaxation. This is the perfect blend of comfort and style - schedule your showing today!
